content:
[[iftags +版式]]
[[module CSS]]
@import url(https://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/theme:3law/code/1);
[[/module]]

这是为[[[third-law-hub|第三定律]]]设定所制作的变体版式。

在你的作品开头添加如下语法以应用此版式：

> @@[[include :scp-wiki-cn:theme:3law]]@@
> @@[[include :scp-wiki-cn:theme:3lawcracked]]@@

[[code type="css"]]
/*
    Cracked Third Law Theme
    [2018 Wikidot Theme]
    A variant of the Third Law Theme created by TyGently.
    Original theme created by GreenWolf, with technical assistance from Randomini and aesthetic assistance from Dr Kens and tawny.
    Based on SCP Sigma 9 Theme created by Aelanna and Dr Devan.
    The Station font was created by Nick Matavka and is licensed under the SIL Open Font License.
    The Prometheus Labs/Third Law Flame Logo was created by GreenWolf and is licensed under CC-BY-SA 3.0.
     Revised by stormbreath.
*/

div#container-wrap {
    background-image: url(http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/theme%3A3lawcracked/body_bg_cracked.png);
}

/* HEADER */
#header {
    background-image: url(http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/theme%3A3lawcracked/crackedbase.gif);
}

#header h2 span::before {
    content: '有些不对劲…';
    font-style: italic;
}
[[/code]]
[[/iftags]]

[[module CSS]]
@import url(https://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/theme:3lawcracked/code/1);
[[/module]]
